well, you know, because we get the prosperity gospel: "Well, we can sow this and I'm going to get five Rolexes, I'm going to get a Ferrari, I'm going to get a Rolls-Royce, and I'm going to get my brand new Gulfstream."I don't think there's anything wrong with having nice things.

